<!-- 
    "HOLLYWHOOD" STYLE PROFILE CODE
    BY PANDAPPUCCINO
    
    == WHAT IS THIS? ==
    Who remembers the era of Tumblr RP where if you could edit a Hollywhood theme with a snazzy background, you were considered the "cool kid" in the RP community?
    
    This code is meant to replicate that vibe, using a background image for the main design. The code page includes the template for the code, with colored sections for each box. It's a simple little "ID card" style profile that you can make as fancy as you want with just an image!
    
    This code is not 100% mobile friendly due to it using absolute sizes and positioning. I tried to keep it small enough that it would fit on mobile screens, however.
    
    == HOW DO I USE IT? ==
    1) Create your background image using the provided template. The template is automatically sized to fit within the constraints of the box itself.
    
    2) Set the background image in the CSS to use the background you made. It will automatically size itself to 100%.
    
    3) Fill out the profile section and set up the links!
    
    == WHAT'S THE CATCH? ==
    Just keep my credit intact; that's all I ask.
	
-->
<div class="container" style="width:650px;
                              height:450px;
                              background:url('');
                              background-size:100%;
                              background-position:center;
                              background-repeat:no-repeat;
                              box-sizing:border-box;
                              border:3px solid white;
                              padding:0">
